      "size": 37296,
      "text": "这是帕斯卡三角，也叫杨辉三角，一个看起来再简单不过的数字表。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pascal-triangle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pascal-triangle/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "顶上是 1，每个数都等于它上方两个数之和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pascal-triangle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pascal-triangle/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "可就是这么简单的规则，藏着一个惊人的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pascal-triangle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pascal-triangle/yunxi/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
